      • thereWasNoQueue

        public void thereWasNoQueue(Customer item)
        The method removeFirst takes the person that is first in line in the queue and creates a CustomerPays event for that person. This also means that the freeRegisters decreases by one and so does the lengthOfQueue variable. throws a NoSuchElementException if there is no Customer in the FIFO

        item- - an item of type Customer
